{"tid":2451432,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"超過7萬2千人附議！國家英雄雕像遭縱火撤下 智利網友聯署換成《進擊的巨人》里維兵長","createTime":"2021-03-18T05:51:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T05:01:31.000Z","uid":4618,"like":54,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"699874fe02fb18a4f2cc242d58e221e8475e7869","tid":2451432,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T05:51:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://game.nownews.com/news/20210318/3290725/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgame.nownews.com%2Fnews%2F20210318%2F3290725%2F&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2fY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=464c5a0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://game.nownews.com/news/20210318/3290725/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0UTVMRN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0UTVMRN.png&h=33d13f3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n南美洲國家智利的人民，近期在連署網站《<a href=\"http://change.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchange.org&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2fY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=b2ba12f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">change.org</a>》發起了一項奇特的連署活動，因為內容竟然是請願政府將智利前總統、同時也是知名將軍的「巴克達諾雕像」替換成《進擊的巨人》中的角色里維兵長，該連署活動已經超過7萬2千人附議。<br />\n<br />\n為什麼要把智利英雄「巴克達諾雕像」換掉呢？起因是近期智利人民發起了抗議示威活動。而在3月5號的示威中，位於聖地牙哥市義大利廣場的巴克達諾雕像被一群不知名人士縱火，這起縱火事件中有63人被捕、7名警察受傷。而智利政府也決定把巴克達諾雕像撤下，以免雕像受到更進一步的傷害。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W5ZmHqr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW5ZmHqr.jpg&h=c4e2e4c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n既然原本巴克達諾雕像的位置空了出來，智利人民就開始思考要放誰的雕像才能彰顯智利人民勇敢、跨越困境的情操。名叫 Denise Flores 的智利女網友就想到了《進擊的巨人》中的里維兵長，認為他有資格成為義大利廣場的新雕像。<br />\n<br />\nDenise Flores 在聯署網頁中表示：「讓我們給這位世界上最強大的軍人一個該有的認可，他在調查兵團內艱苦奮鬥、吃盡了苦頭。把雕像換成我們美麗的的里維兵長吧！」並附上一張位在作者諫山創家鄉日本日田站的里維雕像照片。連署自3月6日發起至截止期間累積7萬2千人參與，離達當初設立的門檻7萬5千人只差一點點就能達標。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jyFtnqz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjyFtnqz.jpg&h=b2f6ca6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日媒《livedoor》指出，智利當地媒體報導此連署後，也受到智利網友的熱烈回復，「很棒的點子」、「里維是全世界最強的男人所以很相襯」、「《七龍珠》的悟空更適合吧」；但也有認真的網友提出反對意見，認為「這想法很愚蠢」、「必須要是跟歷史有關的才行」、「雕像必須要是紀念先民的才行」。<br />\n<br />\n當然，這很明顯只是一個惡搞的連署活動，不過也讓人見識到《進擊的巨人》在南美洲的影響力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/municipalidad-de-santiago-cambiar-la-estatua-de-baquedano-por-una-de-levi-ackerman\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fmunicipalidad-de-santiago-cambiar-la-estatua-de-baquedano-por-una-de-levi-ackerman&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2fY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=1083c780\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/municipalidad-de-santiago-cambiar-la-estatua-de-baquedano-por-una-de-levi-ackerman</a>"},{"pid":"c016d8e3deb4ec89ebea2812d8436863078cbd7d","tid":2451432,"uid":84037,"like":18,"dislike":19,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T05:51:54.000Z","msg":"on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00bb3cd02e40473bccf1f8509814ef78dadb79e3","tid":2451432,"uid":58630,"like":39,"dislike":5,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T05:53:08.000Z","msg":"不如換多啦A夢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"241ec40184d42a93ac2cc682a8e77485ef7e511a","tid":2451432,"uid":105678,"like":7,"dislike":100,"score":-93,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T05:54:25.000Z","msg":"幾好，如果係中國動漫，一定畀人話文化入侵，但日本仔有美國佬護持，點都唔會有人敢正面屌"},{"pid":"1bdae6c30293d982d93a50a56630377d71b98777","tid":2451432,"uid":197640,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"241ec40184d42a93ac2cc682a8e77485ef7e511a","tid":2451432,"uid":105678,"like":7,"dislike":100,"score":-93,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T05:54:25.000Z","msg":"幾好，如果係中國動漫，一定畀人話文化入侵，但日本仔有美國佬護持，點都唔會有人敢正面屌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T05:55:00.000Z","msg":"又一隻五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5d4b92b8396706409ba0590c0e1